  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed development would result in a poor standard of accommodation to the detriment of the amenities of future occupiers due to inadequate internal space. Flat 4 and Flat 1 would fail to provide an acceptable standard of residential accommodation and living space resulting in a cramped and unsatisfactory standard of accommodation to the detriment of the amenities of future occupiers. The proposals would therefore be contrary to policy D6 of the London Plan 2021, CS 14 in the Merton Core Strategy 2011, London Plan 2021 policy D6, Policy DM D2 of the Merton Sites and Policies Plan 2014 and DCLG Technical Housing Standards -nationally described space standard 2015 The proposals would fail to comply with policy DM D2 of the Merton Sites and Policies Plan (2014) and Policy D6 of the London Plan (2021) ",
    "Reason : 2 - In the absence of a site specific flood risk assessment commensurate to the nature and scale of the development due to the siting in an area of Critical Drainage the scheme is considered to increase risk of flooding in the locality contrary to the aims and objections of, in particular, London Plan policy SI 13, Merton Core Strategy (2011) policy CS16 and Merton Sites and Policies Plan (2014) policies DM F1 and DM F2.  ",
    "Reason : 3 - In the absence of satisfactory refuse and recycling facilities, the scheme is considered to adversely impact on the free flow of traffic to the detriment of highway and pedestrian safety contrary to, in particular, the London Plan (2021) Policy SI 7 and Merton's Core Strategy (2011) Policy CS 17. "
  ],
